{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2014/03/still-persist/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/knowledge/","name":"见闻杂事"}],"tags":[{"name":"上海","path":"/tag/shanghai/"},{"name":"坚持","path":"/tag/persistence/"},{"name":"打工","path":"/tag/working/"},{"name":"旅游","path":"/tag/travel/"},{"name":"星宇放映","path":"/tag/xinyu-film/"},{"name":"朋友","path":"/tag/friends/"},{"name":"武汉","path":"/tag/wuhan/"},{"name":"独立影片","path":"/tag/independent-film/"},{"name":"纪录片","path":"/tag/documentary/"},{"name":"自由的家猫","path":"/tag/awildpetcat/"},{"name":"长江商报","path":"/tag/yangtzs-business-daily/"}],"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3cb534315b5f837b77c2e71b886813ac/e737e/IMG_20140328_130800.jpg","srcSet":"/static/3cb534315b5f837b77c2e71b886813ac/e737e/IMG_20140328_130800.jpg 800w,\n/static/3cb534315b5f837b77c2e71b886813ac/5bb6f/IMG_20140328_130800.jpg 1600w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3cb534315b5f837b77c2e71b886813ac/e7773/IMG_20140328_130800.webp 800w,\n/static/3cb534315b5f837b77c2e71b886813ac/f2fb1/IMG_20140328_130800.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}},"path":"/2014/03/still-persist/","date":"2014-03-30T12:41:00.000Z","excerpt":"连续第4天被5：30的闹钟吵醒，起床查看一条刘雯特色的短信——发于临晨3点钟，告知就纪录片《自由的家猫》采访我 … ","title":"还在坚持呆在武汉的日子","content":"<p>连续第4天被5：30的闹钟吵醒，起床查看一条刘雯特色的短信——发于临晨3点钟，告知就纪录片《自由的家猫》采访我的文章，如期刊登于今天的<a href=\"http://www.changjiangtimes.com/szb/20140328/a26.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">长江商报锐读栏目</a>。这标题是我从<a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/2012/back-with-honor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">北京领奖回来后博文</a>内写的，我已经忘记曾写过这样的话，刘雯说她是看到这句话后才决定要采访我。<a href=\"http://www.changjiangtimes.com/szb/20140328/a26.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1444\" alt=\"2014-03-28长江商报-锐读_by刘雯\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/2014-03-28长江商报-锐读_by刘雯-200x300.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/2014-03-28长江商报-锐读_by刘雯-200x300.jpg 200w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/2014-03-28长江商报-锐读_by刘雯-385x576.jpg 385w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/2014-03-28长江商报-锐读_by刘雯.jpg 1447w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" /></a>难掩内心的喜悦，到办公室找到网上链接发给家人和朋友们，我想他们会为我骄傲的。无趣的工作充斥生活，已经很久没有什么事情让我像这样感到快乐的了。讲述2年前的成绩，虽不值得骄傲，但与记者刘雯的交谈，让我在这糟糕的时候，回忆起曾经的良好状态，并再提醒自己要记得向往要做的事情。</p>\n<p>我把这则报道像日常工作那样<a title=\"宜昌小伙拍纪录片 作品拙朴感人闯大学生电影节\" href=\"http://hb.qq.com/a/20140328/017225.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">复制粘贴到大楚网上</a>，然后继续同大家一起严肃认真的做愚蠢、可笑的工作。</p>\n<p>我高兴的把消息分享给徐刚，他也分享一篇文章我——<a href=\"http://wufazhuce.com/one/vol.537#articulo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">把时间浪费在美好的事物上</a>，一下不出声的笑，一下流泪的看完后，终于让我在浮躁、迷失之下得到一点释怀，突然欣然接受自己的孤独、怪癖、单纯，坦诚面对我肿成三眼皮的左上眼皮和一额头的痘痘。中午买一盒饭，到东湖边找一个僻静处，用文字记录这些感触，我就喜欢独自一人在鸟鸣、绿草、大树、蓝天中。<a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140328_130800.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1445\" alt=\"IMG_20140328_130800\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140328_130800-300x225.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140328_130800-300x225.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140328_130800-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>覃雯懿有天突然发短信说“你看似有计划的在做一些事，实际上随波逐流的在瞎搞，什么都想尝试，找不到自己的路”，也许她是看透真实的我。</p>\n<p>一次为朋友拍活动上认识闵晓芳，一个同样爱摄影、做设计，关注点很小众，强大、有内涵、聪明的家伙，还是夷陵区的同乡。逛东湖灯会，夜晚拍照片，手机果然还是不行。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140316_201933.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1446\" alt=\"IMG_20140316_201933\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140316_201933-300x225.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140316_201933-300x225.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140316_201933-768x576.jpg 768w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140316_201933.jpg 1012w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>3月14、15日，上海聚徐刚、曾新达、郭得羊，我们讲述各自的生活，分享所见所想，还有三峡晚报的同事杨梦竹妹妹，独闯上海滩。短暂的相聚后又各奔东西，你们都是我的榜样！祝福我们大家。<a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mmexport1394898067809.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1447\" alt=\"mmexport1394898067809\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mmexport1394898067809-300x225.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mmexport1394898067809-300x225.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mmexport1394898067809-768x576.jpg 768w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mmexport1394898067809.jpg 1012w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_6996.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1450\" alt=\"CBL_6996\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_6996-300x198.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_6996-300x198.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_6996-870x576.jpg 870w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_6996.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>还有去看内幕重重的选秀活动，梦瑶依然是最棒的！如今拍照片没有全神贯注、不段寻找角度、等待瞬间、所有参数了如指掌的状态，很久没用的Nikkor 55-200mm镜头防抖坏掉又长酶。我简直糟透了。<a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_7197_1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1449\" alt=\"CBL_7197_1\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_7197_1-198x300.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_7197_1-198x300.jpg 198w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_7197_1-381x576.jpg 381w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/CBL_7197_1.jpg 530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 198px) 100vw, 198px\" /></a>两度回宜昌更正身份证信息，办台湾通行证，回家看欢喜和花花，这母子俩可开心了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140324_081121.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"IMG_20140324_081121\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_20140324_081121-300x225.jpg\"/></a>还在坚持呆在武汉的日子，生活的大部分是无脑复制粘贴的工作，和3年前搜房的日子有点相似，也就是说有时间开展新的个人项目了，下一步就是在武汉安置一个良好的工作环境。</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2014/03/still-persist/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}